<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-577-500  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 577 500.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  August 8 1989 v3 n29 p5(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT MacWEEK Inc. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>CE's DiskTop 4.0 speeds launches. (CE Software) (productannouncement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Norr, Henry.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   CE Software Inc. (product introduction).andO;Product:   CE Software DiskTop 4.0 (computer program) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionUtility ProgramsFile ManagementSoftware Packages.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>CE's DiskTop 4.0 speeds launchesandM;West Des Moines, Iowa -- CE Software will roll out DiskTop 4.0, a majorupgrade to one of the most widely used Mac desk accessories, at his week'sMacworld Expo.andM;The new release, due in late September, will add dozens of new features tothe Finder substitute/complement.andP;  Among them are:andM;* A new launching utility accessible at any time, with or withoutMultiFinder, either from a submenu at the top of the Apple menu or via aconfigurable hot key.andP;  Suers will be able to install an unlimited number ofapplications and documents.andM;* Enhanced file-finding capabilities, also available directly from the Applemenu or hot keys.andP;  Searching is much faster than in earlier versions, CEsaid, and the list of files found is retained so that users can act on themin a batch.andM;* Pop-up menus for drive selection without tabbing through all mountedvolumes, Command-key equivalents for virtually all fenctions, a New Folderbutton in Copy and Move dialogs, and a variety of other enhancements.andM;GOfer 2.0, a new version of the $79.95 text search -and-retrieval utilityfrom Microlytics of Pittsford, N.Y., will be bundled with DiskTop 4.0 (seeMacWEEK, Aug. 1).andM;&quot;Calling DiskTop 4.0 a good file-handling utility is like calling a Porschejust a faster kind of horse,&quot; said beta tester Andy Clay of Brian Supply Co.andO;in Providence, R.I.andP;  &quot;What amazed me is that once you find the file or filesyou're looking for, you can copy, delete, move and set AppleShare privilegeson the whole bunch.andP;  With one click of the mouse you can even have the Macopen them all using the application they were created in.&quot;andM;DiskTop's price will double to $99.95.andP;  Upgrades will be $30 to currentowners and $15 to those who buy Version 3.0 between now and the time the newrelease ships.andM;CE Software is at 1854 Fuller Road, P.O. Box 65580, West Des Moines, Iowa50265; (515) 224-1995.andO;</TEXT></DOC>